Thank you so much for coming.

01:02:01.000 --> 01:02:02.000
&gt;&gt;Nancy Schulman: Thank you.

01:02:02.000 --> 01:02:03.000
Thank you.

01:02:03.000 --> 01:02:04.000
&gt;&gt;Ellen Birnbaum: Thank you for having us.

